metadata.name: The Resurrection of the Sacred Feminine
metadata.description:
It is through art, the language of symbols and emotion that we will ignite the sacred feminine, join me as we resurrect the divine,  liberate human emotion, and transcend into the next evolutionary step of mankind, the masculofeminine sapien.

4000px X 2633px
